OL,3,CHusband and wife tried to murder
OL,4,Cstepmother in household row
OL,6,FA young couple from Birmingham have
OL,7,Fbeen found guilty of trying to murder
OL,8,Ftheir stepmother after they attacked
OL,9,Fher with a hammer and a knife.
OL,11,FNabela Tabassum, 19 and Wasif Hussain,
OL,12,F21, wore animal masks before ambushing
OL,13,FArifa Nazmin at their family home in
OL,14,FMidhurst Road, Kings Norton on January
OL,15,F29.
OL,17,FThe couple were found guilty of
OL,18,Fattempted murder at Birmingham Crown
OL,19,FCourt on March 27.
