OL,3,CHusband and wife tried to murder
OL,4,Cstepmother in household row
OL,6,FHussain burst into tears as the jury
OL,7,Fdelivered their verdict, Tabassum was
OL,8,Falso convicted of the same offence.
OL,10,FFootage from inside the house shows
OL,11,FHussain hitting her with the hammer
OL,12,Fbefore strangling and repeatedly
OL,13,Fpunching her.
OL,15,FArifa suffered a stab wound to her arm
OL,16,Fas she tried to defend herself and
OL,17,Fmanaged to survive the attack after
OL,18,Fconvincing the couple to let her go
OL,19,Fupstairs, where she then called the
OL,20,Fpolice.
