OL,4,Cstepmother in household row
OL,6,FAfter the attack, they both fled
OL,7,FBirmingham and were arrested by police
OL,8,Fat a travelodge in Bolton in the early
OL,9,Fhours of the following day.
OL,11,FThe court heard how the pair met
OL,12,Fonline in 2023. Their families
OL,13,Farranged for them to marry that year
OL,14,Fafter learning of their relationship.
OL,16,FTabassum came to live permanently with
OL,17,FHussain in Kings Norton in the home he
OL,18,Fshared with his father Mohammed
OL,19,FHussain and stepmother Mrs Nazmin.
