OL,6,FA trial heard the atmosphere quickly
OL,7,Fturned toxic with Mrs Nazmin accusing
OL,8,Fthe couple of using the home like a
OL,9,F'hotel'.
OL,11,FShe also complained Tabassum did not
OL,12,Fwash up properly and called her
OL,13,Fparents who told their daughter she
OL,14,Fmust adjust to her in-laws.
OL,16,FIn the days before they attacked Mrs
OL,17,FNazmin the couple bought animal masks
OL,18,Ffrom Poundland as well as a lighter
OL,19,Fand aerosol can from a shop.
