OL,3,CHusband and wife tried to murder
OL,4,Cstepmother in household row
OL,6,FHe claimed he only wanted to "scare"
OL,7,FMrs Nazmin. Tabassum had already
OL,8,Fadmitted inflicting grievous bodily
OL,9,Fharm with intent.
OL,11,FShe denied wanting to kill the victim
OL,12,Fand claimed she followed the
OL,13,Finstructions of her husband because
OL,14,Fshe was "scared".
OL,16,FThey will be sentenced on 21 May after
OL,17,Fprobation and psychiatric assessments
OL,18,Fare carried out.
